data.name: textBox1.Text
data.value: iSafePDF is a free open source software that allow you to sign, encrypt and modify PDF meta-data. It uses the excellent iTextSharp Library (itextsharp.sourceforge.net) to do PDF manipulations. The full source code of this program is available for download at this url : feel free to contact me for any bug or suggestion
